{"inkVersion":21,"root":[[{"->":"opening"},["done",{"#f":5,"#n":"g-0"}],null],"done",{"opening":["^$DISABLE_ALL_ACTIONS ","#","^auto:true","/#","\n","^$SLEEP:8 ","#","^auto:true","/#","\n","^我是磷光，是灯塔「磷光」的守塔人。 ","#","^type:SubtitleText ","/#","#","^skippable:false ","/#","#","^auto:true ","/#","#","^sleep:1.5 ","/#","#","^duration:3","/#","\n","^14 岁那年，父亲把灯塔的钥匙、连着「磷光」这个名字一并传给了我。 ","#","^type:SubtitleText ","/#","#","^skippable:false ","/#","#","^auto:true ","/#","#","^sleep:1.5 ","/#","#","^duration:5","/#","\n","^从那时起我便独自一人维护这灯塔至今。 ","#","^type:SubtitleText ","/#","#","^skippable:false ","/#","#","^auto:true ","/#","#","^sleep:1.5 ","/#","#","^duration:3","/#","\n","^或许听到灯塔，许多人的第一反应是好奇或者疑惑。 ","#","^type:SubtitleText ","/#","#","^skippable:false ","/#","#","^auto:true ","/#","#","^sleep:1.5 ","/#","#","^duration:3.5","/#","\n","^这毕竟是个无线电普及的时代，灯塔正逐渐退出历史的舞台。 ","#","^type:SubtitleText ","/#","#","^skippable:false ","/#","#","^auto:true ","/#","#","^sleep:1.5 ","/#","#","^duration:5","/#","\n","^人们早就不再兴建灯塔了，现存的灯塔也逐渐被废弃。 ","#","^type:SubtitleText ","/#","#","^skippable:false ","/#","#","^auto:true ","/#","#","^sleep:1.2 ","/#","#","^duration:4","/#","\n","^它们是鲜活的坟茔—— ","#","^type:SubtitleText ","/#","#","^skippable:false ","/#","#","^auto:true ","/#","#","^sleep:1","/#","\n","^而我大概会是这坟茔的最后一任扫墓人。 ","#","^type:SubtitleText ","/#","#","^skippable:false ","/#","#","^auto:true ","/#","#","^sleep:3 ","/#","#","^duration:3","/#","\n","^只是，我时常想，灯塔与卫星信号毕竟是不一样的。 ","#","^type:SubtitleText ","/#","#","^skippable:false ","/#","#","^auto:true ","/#","#","^sleep:1.5 ","/#","#","^duration:3","/#","\n","^身在夜晚黑暗而沉默的海的时候，怀疑与恐惧带来的窒息感会一寸寸扼紧咽喉。 ","#","^type:SubtitleText ","/#","#","^skippable:false ","/#","#","^auto:true ","/#","#","^sleep:2 ","/#","#","^duration:5","/#","\n","^但倘若，此时突然有一束光刺破重重黑暗，向着自己的双眼奔来。 ","#","^type:SubtitleText ","/#","#","^skippable:false ","/#","#","^auto:true ","/#","#","^sleep:1.5 ","/#","#","^duration:4","/#","\n","^所有人都会瞬间明白，那就是家的方向。 ","#","^type:SubtitleText ","/#","#","^skippable:false ","/#","#","^auto:true ","/#","#","^sleep:1.5","/#","\n","^这才是灯塔无可替代的地方。 ","#","^type:SubtitleText ","/#","#","^skippable:false ","/#","#","^auto:true ","/#","#","^sleep:3","/#","\n","^$ENABLE_ALL_ACTIONS","\n","end",{"#f":1}],"#f":1}],"listDefs":{}}